{"tid":391143,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"跳槽去新公司,應否內疚","createTime":"2017-09-07T14:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T07:05:45.000Z","uid":53413,"like":518,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34d60b32775679a96984fdcbff055921fdc95c63","tid":391143,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"捱多一個星期<br />\n就跳槽去新公司<br />\n但係舊公司已經唔夠人<br />\n而家對住同事,老細 有D內疚 <br />\n老細仲極力唔加人工咁留我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁用人情牌話做生不如做熟<br />\n新公司出offer 多4k <br />\n<br />\n我只係個職場新仔,而家仲係好內疚<br />\n係唔係好撚傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37871b033311d49aeaf5e2d7dccabdf3834d4ac9","tid":391143,"uid":27708,"like":600,"dislike":2,"score":598,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"無人工加=同你講笑<br />\n人情當飯食？"},{"pid":"0b0062bce8dcc17dcb6a85d2c64eb74c835117bf","tid":391143,"uid":58247,"like":251,"dislike":2,"score":249,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捱多一個星期<br />\n就跳槽去新公司<br />\n但係舊公司已經唔夠人<br />\n而家對住同事,老細 有D內疚 <br />\n老細仲極力唔加人工咁留我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁用人情牌話做生不如做熟<br />\n新公司出offer 多4k <br />\n<br />\n我只係個職場新仔,而家仲係好內疚<br />\n係唔係好撚傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係有誠意會唔加人工?打工唔係為錢唔通真係為興趣咩"},{"pid":"15792c9646235ec79c102b5ed58d0c2cb6dc6fa7","tid":391143,"uid":126831,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:33:45.000Z","msg":"新公司多4k,點會唔轉"},{"pid":"5c278f8aea31f0e83b3fa65368e31788906d9f12","tid":391143,"uid":77905,"like":94,"dislike":0,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"職場無真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52838057e23a1def5116706b31b5b3fea34f6978","tid":391143,"uid":101733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"邊行？"},{"pid":"223e817c61ed6015e7b35f0197088dd2f857f3ac","tid":391143,"uid":70008,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捱多一個星期<br />\n就跳槽去新公司<br />\n但係舊公司已經唔夠人<br />\n而家對住同事,老細 有D內疚 <br />\n老細仲極力唔加人工咁留我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁用人情牌話做生不如做熟<br />\n新公司出offer 多4k <br />\n我只係個職場新仔,而家仲係好內疚<br />\n係唔係好撚傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舊公司連4k都加唔到，有乜嘢好内疚。 你老闆而家就好似D人喺度間舖頭同個老闆打人情牌， 求個老闆平啲賣嘢畀佢。而家呢就係個雜貨舖老闆，你話你會點做呀"},{"pid":"3be7e8b0acb960aebf257348d93815de5c1ee806","tid":391143,"uid":140875,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"人工先係最大保障"},{"pid":"fce8f267d40e999ccbfa82234e53378dde60f294","tid":391143,"uid":134864,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"打工講感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a13904f63f20c8a0f653ed34e20b4064f3029f3","tid":391143,"uid":38318,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"過兩日就唔記得你啦"},{"pid":"e7585f6687719980cfcac9820cd16b34ac4edd59","tid":391143,"uid":10296,"like":158,"dislike":0,"score":158,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"同你講個故事<br />\n我初初做第一份工個陣啲同事扮晒family咁<br />\n之後因為我毒撚格做事唔順利，同事見我拖後腿就即刻態度180度轉變<br />\n最尾新年前炒埋魷魚<br />\n<br />\n你舊公司挽留你純粹因為你有利用價值"},{"pid":"c61cd5d5de58e4814453faf8490f21a346839303","tid":391143,"uid":24617,"like":123,"dislike":1,"score":122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"極力唔加人工咁留你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為你打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5a69b9de2118d624fa1ee05f7400a71667cda4","tid":391143,"uid":9148,"like":131,"dislike":2,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"10皮野加4k咁就諗下走唔走都好正常<br />\n但二三萬加4K 就唔算少架啦<br />\n一毫都唔加就想留人，係咪你老細當你係on9,定係你真係on9先？"},{"pid":"1e4ae6e4b7a0530b60ac9c5b933109a8ff077fe3","tid":391143,"uid":29982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"新公司offer多8k"},{"pid":"9f75fa948ec93aac088e8c10c192dfb99ec50f81","tid":391143,"uid":96146,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"新公司人工多4k 你仲唔明自己係舊公司既廉價奴工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffbe8c184c90921edf1fee886411cd6e0dc65db","tid":391143,"uid":13809,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"一間公司唔會話無左邊個唔得"},{"pid":"045fa04de7fe5112e4b24dbac72e3f1b20dbe37a","tid":391143,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"做過份惡頂工，每日都係折磨，頂唔順想走，一個月通知，咁啱又有同事走，老細叫我做落去，一路揾一路做，但我都係留多兩個月就quit"},{"pid":"7ebbb908c751b06b1148fa9510a5f0c4fcb10738","tid":391143,"uid":53413,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:18:20.000Z","msg":"明白<br />\n唔該晒咁多位巴絲打  <br />\n我諗我係職場講感情<br />\n真係好ON9  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5594e805f661437117b816d7092a87a07a38e38c","tid":391143,"uid":65818,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捱多一個星期<br />\n就跳槽去新公司<br />\n但係舊公司已經唔夠人<br />\n而家對住同事,老細 有D內疚 <br />\n老細仲極力唔加人工咁留我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁用人情牌話做生不如做熟<br />\n新公司出offer 多4k <br />\n<br />\n我只係個職場新仔,而家仲係好內疚<br />\n係唔係好撚傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n命就得一條<br />\n當你廿歲<br />\n三十歲前嘅時間得3650日<br />\n三十歲後你當你唔會再加人工<br />\n仲有可能被炒<br />\n<br />\n後生仔<br />\n你諗吓第時生個仔playgroups都四千蚊一個月你就會諗通<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7decd8daae70bb89845932e458976ad4ceb3a488","tid":391143,"uid":76848,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你講個故事<br />\n我初初做第一份工個陣啲同事扮晒family咁<br />\n之後因為我毒撚格做事唔順利，同事見我拖後腿就即刻態度180度轉變<br />\n最尾新年前炒埋魷魚<br />\n<br />\n你舊公司挽留你純粹因為你有利用價值</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毒撚又拖後腿，做事唔順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到米仲要出人工俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b478ddf76fed96c63bdddad0d2f684e69fa993d1","tid":391143,"uid":135390,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"雖然我知情況差好遠但都想搭單問下<br />\n讀緊書做緊飲食pt得47/hr<br />\n收工番到屋企起碼12點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近揾左另一份係學校入邊做helper有60/hour<br />\n收工番到屋企大概11點<br />\n唔使咁夜訓,第二朝仲有精神上堂<br />\n依家做緊個份本身已經唔夠人做<br />\n如果我走埋會令班同事既工時更長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我之前又同左佢講會一邊讀書一邊做<br />\n每個星期會番到兩三日<br />\n咁如果我依家同老細講唔做會唔會好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答埋先屌我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20179793d40522316125399c5dce42a1b52a5b6","tid":391143,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3739512ad1cb866356ab1a7af270ea591290b84a","tid":391143,"uid":8199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你講個故事<br />\n我初初做第一份工個陣啲同事扮晒family咁<br />\n之後因為我毒撚格做事唔順利，同事見我拖後腿就即刻態度180度轉變<br />\n最尾新年前炒埋魷魚<br />\n<br />\n你舊公司挽留你純粹因為你有利用價值</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毒撚又拖後腿，做事唔順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到米仲要出人工俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁撚廢仲要大聲講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c293aedf88e411958c97ff49fde43845ab3387d","tid":391143,"uid":85819,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77fee12047257e54fe2fce91cbdebe179d7db7b2","tid":391143,"uid":5715,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"打工為賺錢，邊到人工高就去邊，洗撚內疚"},{"pid":"bb3494afb59e316c8ee97ef7d71c91e9b2bd06f8","tid":391143,"uid":53413,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要求加人工老闆拒絕果陣唔知有冇心痛呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係職場新仔<br />\n人工都唔敢要求加 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89656b49795456c0352cb23b4459d6c4689c9395","tid":391143,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"打份工唔講錢唔通講感情呀？"},{"pid":"ddae4b3d8ab7e2269172264dec3f39ad10cbd870","tid":391143,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10皮野加4k咁就諗下走唔走都好正常<br />\n但二三萬加4K 就唔算少架啦<br />\n一毫都唔加就想留人，係咪你老細當你係on9,定係你真係on9先？</blockquote><br />\n睇完樓主篇嘢都問得出邊個on9<br />\n睇嚟你先係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226cdfddab91ba7eaec4eebe26d21e07fcdd98ea","tid":391143,"uid":34419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我知情況差好遠但都想搭單問下<br />\n讀緊書做緊飲食pt得47/hr<br />\n收工番到屋企起碼12點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近揾左另一份係學校入邊做helper有60/hour<br />\n收工番到屋企大概11點<br />\n唔使咁夜訓,第二朝仲有精神上堂<br />\n依家做緊個份本身已經唔夠人做<br />\n如果我走埋會令班同事既工時更長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我之前又同左佢講會一邊讀書一邊做<br />\n每個星期會番到兩三日<br />\n咁如果我依家同老細講唔做會唔會好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答埋先屌我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪話返工兼顧唔到兩邊囉 炒佢魷魚啦 唔通佢同你講你應承咗佢留係度做咩"},{"pid":"6f54a300fa3e3e823d4cc463f518d88ddc1762bd","tid":391143,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d50a41de5141576a0d924a3cb94e66c3a409c42d","tid":391143,"uid":35370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"你記住，你係勞工嚟咋<br />\n同男人叫雞一樣，講錢唔講感情架"},{"pid":"7fc101ba8513bfc0d103bf9638557a8a676c2fe0","tid":391143,"uid":27210,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"舊時做細公司個老細唔加人工兼屌住咁留我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88ddd8352410bd6ca6460290168ac951a7e6215","tid":391143,"uid":80598,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊時做細公司個老細唔加人工兼屌住咁留我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲公司永遠都喺唔夠人手嗰時先知驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a71f91580d728305a73c5f99074752050c8290c","tid":391143,"uid":60020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"唔加人工想留到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0650275b1ed569e4df2a31ce4b9e3e9d1a8acde1","tid":391143,"uid":58393,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我知情況差好遠但都想搭單問下<br />\n讀緊書做緊飲食pt得47/hr<br />\n收工番到屋企起碼12點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近揾左另一份係學校入邊做helper有60/hour<br />\n收工番到屋企大概11點<br />\n唔使咁夜訓,第二朝仲有精神上堂<br />\n依家做緊個份本身已經唔夠人做<br />\n如果我走埋會令班同事既工時更長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我之前又同左佢講會一邊讀書一邊做<br />\n每個星期會番到兩三日<br />\n咁如果我依家同老細講唔做會唔會好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答埋先屌我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n永遠唔好覺得自己係衰人<br />\n如果有人出2萬蚊請你啲同事過檔<br />\n你啲同事一定諗都唔洗諗即走"},{"pid":"c1551fabeb409043664809223ec1d0408d3b8553","tid":391143,"uid":58393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"樓主讀書讀到咩程度？"},{"pid":"3936756d6e60a5562706bf3b0c0b87206f608342","tid":391143,"uid":12731,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"純粹因為唔夠人嘅話無乜好內疚，你又唔係即日通知一穫kiu起佢，無咩好良心責備。<br />\n<br />\n反而有邊啲同事對過你好嘅話，你好好咁同佢地道別，我諗佢地就算唔捨得你都會祝福你前程錦繡。至於個老闆... 算啦老闆呢家野，仲要唔肯加人工比你嘅老闆<br />\n<br />\n返工始終都要講錢，你講到自己初入職場咁，咁差4k應該都真係差好遠，所以走啦，唔使覺得內疚，輕輕的我帶走一片雲彩，唔好諗到自己咁重要，呢個世界無話邊個無左邊個唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4499230ccf7c119c8b044bb80bc79022c5310caf","tid":391143,"uid":27049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"已經唔夠人仲想唔加人工留人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇呢個老細都撈唔掂啦留低都無好日子過"},{"pid":"7890c6949a5884768beb7af7d64f77c690ac579a","tid":391143,"uid":47470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"唔捨得好同事好過啦<br />\n香港地老細好極有個譜，錢點都重要過你班撚樣"},{"pid":"5823b1d6709654c354a61d671a24f35a651a7fa3","tid":391143,"uid":11895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"啲老細個個都仆街黎<br />\n唔同佢地講人工講心咩屌你"},{"pid":"2dc038f8639c659aa52fef61ca75154132f4cd3a","tid":391143,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:18:11.000Z","msg":"你不如唔好收人工同你老細打一世工 <br />\n極力唔加人工咁留你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身份工肯定冇錢冇前途或者惡哽 唔係點會唔夠人用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d71beaf9274ac4769cf262076964d7bf4b2947c","tid":391143,"uid":97550,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:19:01.000Z","msg":"開咗底牌比人知你想走，就算你最後選擇留低都肯撚定冇好日子過 \\ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> /"},{"pid":"a74229ec558a73f75f74172ca76ae2b08af76943","tid":391143,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:19:02.000Z","msg":"e 個年代<br />\n咩都講錢. <br />\n<br />\n除非你e 家間公司好有潛力就話姐."},{"pid":"216a9ce9acee76bfa5677da34f5867318e40991f","tid":391143,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊時做細公司個老細唔加人工兼屌住咁留我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08058a732fb13148dca090a903783bb7e8a26b66","tid":391143,"uid":62996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:20:11.000Z","msg":"差4k差好遠喎<br />\n舊老細留你但冇話加你人工，根本唔洗猶豫<br />\n比足通知期，交接好就完成責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走左又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公司又唔會執既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3da86f54e7b2026f156078525b7ea6cba9f5a5d","tid":391143,"uid":53413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"大家句句都金石良言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臨走個日<br />\n唯有請d 同事食散水餅先"},{"pid":"fa0b228b71a6522a5c3f7200f72604a1e0047c3a","tid":391143,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:23:58.000Z","msg":"打工唔講錢講感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd09a13bbd4da364cbfc6fac5b0ec0f6b81833ec","tid":391143,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:25:23.000Z","msg":"