工時更長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我之前又同左佢講會一邊讀書一邊做<br />\n每個星期會番到兩三日<br />\n咁如果我依家同老細講唔做會唔會好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答埋先屌我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求其講話要返學就得<br />\n你仲係學生，唔會為難你既<br />\n返學係最大理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7320c196dedc4d7019d8870d5d4937686b81b66c","tid":391143,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d36314c17852586130bb595bf5fdc7c88ffb50","tid":391143,"uid":37976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"不應<br />\n<br />\n四千都加唔到 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50ee0a62ba77e5afb0dc49ca1f2961735f28706","tid":391143,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T19:12:00.000Z","msg":"唔夠人用都係公司問題<br />\n即係人工低/惡啃, 無人肯做<br />\n得你地幾個傻仔做<br />\n你地唔出聲 咪1個頂2個囉<br />\n使咩走去請多啲人返黎?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d522fb092c8d5e9fab050827f0aee40904d9397e","tid":391143,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T19:17:26.000Z","msg":"打工講感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1effb7493352eb5a2ccca67e0a806e2cf4b3048f","tid":391143,"uid":73721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚多岩岩出來做野既小朋友出現係呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩你好有年歷好型啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc8a96bdb7ade4bab8d2865c3e7f4e0966696be","tid":391143,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>極力唔加人工咁留你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為你打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又打得幾好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f29920d28319fdaf6333c7025d28c3797e2b5f","tid":391143,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:28:57.000Z","msg":"我公做緊條team得4條友 黎緊走兩個 你咪樓豬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3c759d01311dfde5ae0d72b250313914840f71","tid":391143,"uid":58046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你講個故事<br />\n我初初做第一份工個陣啲同事扮晒family咁<br />\n之後因為我毒撚格做事唔順利，同事見我拖後腿就即刻態度180度轉變<br />\n最尾新年前炒埋魷魚<br />\n<br />\n你舊公司挽留你純粹因為你有利用價值</blockquote><br />\n正解"},{"pid":"494bf237c44d2ee78b7dd4dd0cfe2263b41f37c6","tid":391143,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:31:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家句句都金石良言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臨走個日<br />\n唯有請d 同事食散水餅先</blockquote><br />\n走果陣散水餅我都無買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d27f7d124b371a64e217f54869a92bca21a881","tid":391143,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:45:44.000Z","msg":"番工唔講錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91565770154b76b399bdc52f8c145408e8e00fa","tid":391143,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a5ce984ee69265beb639b28dc057c8dc9d9383","tid":391143,"uid":66825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:46:55.000Z","msg":"傻喇 唔會有地方係無邊個會死<br />\n你公司過幾個禮拜又係咁"},{"pid":"7e9d6854e761e46c951eca01fe7e94b0116e89fc","tid":391143,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捱多一個星期<br />\n就跳槽去新公司<br />\n但係舊公司已經唔夠人<br />\n而家對住同事,老細 有D內疚 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老細仲極力唔加人工咁留我</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁用人情牌話做生不如做熟<br />\n新公司出offer 多4k <br />\n<br />\n我只係個職場新仔,而家仲係好內疚<br />\n係唔係好撚傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「後生仔，出黎做野唔好咁計較！」"},{"pid":"c75b948bbc44777b2014938c8d7d34ea39c1c376","tid":391143,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻喇 唔會有地方係無邊個會死<br />\n你公司過幾個禮拜又係咁</blockquote><br />\n就算佢執笠都係間公司經營能力有問題<br />\n你做員工冇責任去做陪葬<br />\n唔好咁天真"},{"pid":"d379d21e8b5f27bb28b360cb9f2f43edcfe01853","tid":391143,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:56:58.000Z","msg":"內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你同公司拍拖啊"},{"pid":"17bd9cfbc88bda0c707fd627f913a3454e451793","tid":391143,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我知情況差好遠但都想搭單問下<br />\n讀緊書做緊飲食pt得47/hr<br />\n收工番到屋企起碼12點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近揾左另一份係學校入邊做helper有60/hour<br />\n收工番到屋企大概11點<br />\n唔使咁夜訓,第二朝仲有精神上堂<br />\n依家做緊個份本身已經唔夠人做<br />\n如果我走埋會令班同事既工時更長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我之前又同左佢講會一邊讀書一邊做<br />\n每個星期會番到兩三日<br />\n咁如果我依家同老細講唔做會唔會好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答埋先屌我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專心讀書啦"},{"pid":"07837b27bda67f820e464a8ab7db5b857c20948e","tid":391143,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:58:19.000Z","msg":"同公司講感情，你返第一份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef13c95d726b153f6223eb43bbf6ff9cb6528fe1","tid":391143,"uid":13207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:01:19.000Z","msg":"你打工咋 講感情？<br />\n唔夠人用又點 呢個問題係你老細諗 幾時到你諗"},{"pid":"93e67edcea778f504289b8e241e0f9d55aac71d9","tid":391143,"uid":93713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:04:25.000Z","msg":"Equinix?"},{"pid":"1040113629163254c36812524b4c006335dd9523","tid":391143,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:06:03.000Z","msg":"果陣舊公司留我比新offer多7k都唔留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65be73054efd24573dfb2cc1a8d6a4af0d13b3f9","tid":391143,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同公司講感情，你返第一份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我返第二份工，反而係女上司同我講感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但份工連人工都冇，我彩佢有味"},{"pid":"53e5f872f12596b65b7b8ddd82e14d4b2cf1ca17","tid":391143,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>e 個年代<br />\n咩都講錢. <br />\n<br />\n除非你e 家間公司好有潛力就話姐.</blockquote><br />\n睇潛力咪即係睇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b9e3406bd99b1acb411d64c60e746525b1b6ff","tid":391143,"uid":11108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:19:12.000Z","msg":"巴打我早幾個月同你一樣情況, <br />\n家陣係新公司拎多4成糧係度un un 腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d1e8cd886adea0e8efcdea844a4f43186adff1","tid":391143,"uid":125432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:22:18.000Z","msg":"如果你唔走實玩殘你、因為都預左你會再走"},{"pid":"a75c6cc5b411539acf72802937ac44eb43ccf088","tid":391143,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:23:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a68e1a4c74644c581ba29562401d175e3a29ae5","tid":391143,"uid":31733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:26:50.000Z","msg":"差4k唔洗諗啦，即走啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非間公司包飯又樓下又hea，<br />\n人工都唔加，搵鬼留低咩"},{"pid":"441f34af3686c2523f5bcbb2f2e7b7eae12b31ef","tid":391143,"uid":132873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我知情況差好遠但都想搭單問下<br />\n讀緊書做緊飲食pt得47/hr<br />\n收工番到屋企起碼12點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近揾左另一份係學校入邊做helper有60/hour<br />\n收工番到屋企大概11點<br />\n唔使咁夜訓,第二朝仲有精神上堂<br />\n依家做緊個份本身已經唔夠人做<br />\n如果我走埋會令班同事既工時更長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我之前又同左佢講會一邊讀書一邊做<br />\n每個星期會番到兩三日<br />\n咁如果我依家同老細講唔做會唔會好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答埋先屌我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你問自己，一邊讀書，一邊打工做pt 為咩？ 如果為錢 ...完全唔駛諗啦 ..."},{"pid":"fc76e225378672a6129f7cc3b4a33694c2ac6eb0","tid":391143,"uid":29489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:30:39.000Z","msg":"個人經驗<br />\n佢加人工留你<br />\n如果你留低 你唔駛旨意果幾千蚊可以袋袋平安<br />\n工作量一定加 責任一定加<br />\n對你要求一定高 d<br />\n<br />\nd 仆街，留你果時就苦口婆心<br />\n你留低坐穩之後就開始報復<br />\n到時你走 又要搵過份 未搵到就口口搞你"},{"pid":"4d97458dbc2b855166c5749f3dd783a174308772","tid":391143,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"每個月多4k，接近一個月一部新電話<br />\n要幾傻仔先會講感情"},{"pid":"41eb9518fdfa3425da433d0deeb9bfd5be6e233f","tid":391143,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人經驗<br />\n佢加人工留你<br />\n如果你留低 你唔駛旨意果幾千蚊可以袋袋平安<br />\n工作量一定加 責任一定加<br />\n對你要求一定高 d<br />\n<br />\nd 仆街，留你果時就苦口婆心<br />\n你留低坐穩之後就開始報復<br />\n到時你走 又要搵過份 未搵到就口口搞你</blockquote><br />\n根本就係"},{"pid":"0d50938602266b05ef1a28a0c9851b5e274964cf","tid":391143,"uid":2766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:34:14.000Z","msg":"你有諗過當初跳槽既一定有你既原因<br />\n唔理係老細有幾唔好/公司d人相處唔到<br />\n咁樣就算你夾硬留係舊公司又咪係做得唔開心<br />\n有咩謂?<br />\n<br />\n你老細見唔夠人用緊係留你啦<br />\n你幫佢搞好手頭上既野<br />\n佢請到新人 咪又係一腳伸走你<br />\n新公司啦 唔使考慮咁多<br />\n舊公司佢死佢事 你又無股份<br />\n咁著緊做咩?"},{"pid":"a45beb344a023aae76ea69a8c01c56bcab61020b","tid":391143,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:37:59.000Z","msg":"新仔多4K又唔算多wor<br />\n除非你話係舊公司做得唔耐 e.g. 幾個月貨仔"},{"pid":"4f1057a5b9f1f9876662b1f6b8eea5d08172093d","tid":391143,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>e 個年代<br />\n咩都講錢. <br />\n<br />\n除非你e 家間公司好有潛力就話姐.</blockquote><br />\n睇潛力咪即係睇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先睇前途 後睇人工<br />\n<br />\n無前途比高人工你都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1a6813952ec45f400d2c71eebed2236a957b2f","tid":391143,"uid":31699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你要求加人工老闆拒絕果陣唔知有冇心痛呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係職場新仔<br />\n人工都唔敢要求加 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真 第一份工的人工有幾多 絕對會影響未來搵工個叫價 月薪加4K咁多緊係走啦"},{"pid":"6e2a6d999f3624afd339e2c1df2d5dd957963054","tid":391143,"uid":38609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捱多一個星期<br />\n就跳槽去新公司<br />\n但係舊公司已經唔夠人<br />\n而家對住同事,老細 有D內疚 <br />\n老細仲極力唔加人工咁留我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁用人情牌話做生不如做熟<br />\n新公司出offer 多4k <br />\n<br />\n我只係個職場新仔,而家仲係好內疚<br />\n係唔係好撚傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔加人工留你<br />\n叫佢快撚啲執笠啦"},{"pid":"fdcda71bf7c0fdbc40c11d5fdf15f457b234eb47","tid":391143,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新仔多4K又唔算多wor<br />\n除非你話係舊公司做得唔耐 e.g. 幾個月貨仔</blockquote><br />\n4k都唔算多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我當新仔搵萬2蚊，多4k都多成1/3喎"},{"pid":"121bc0ba11c425f243e3890afa448d42169a7234","tid":391143,"uid":40029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:49:36.000Z","msg":"唔好傻啦，職場唔會有感情"},{"pid":"a825bf53bee51a7a546e77d8c5e893f2746a9ef0","tid":391143,"uid":19062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:50:56.000Z","msg":"應該自己袋四千 其他留黎比舊公司請番個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11311d50c4a0a6a28b2825cec5105c78e9714241","tid":391143,"uid":131548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:51:16.000Z","